<div class="email-block">
  If you have forgotten your password, you may use the following link to
  reset your password.
</div>
<div class="email-block email-block-large">
  <%= link_to "Reset your Password Now", password_reset_url(@user.password_reset_token), class: "button", target: "_blank" %>
</div>
<div class="email-block">
  If you did not request to reset your password, ignore this email
  and nothing will change.
</div>
<div class="email-block">
  If you do not use this link within 2 hours, it will expire.
  After that, you will have to <%= link_to "request a new password reset", new_password_reset_url %>.
</div>
